tags.fixme: Is all of Hall Lane 20mph or just between New Road and the Roundabout?
tags.name: Hall Lane
New Road
tags.note: This is New Road because of postal addresses (the houses on N.R are on this side bit).
When it goes through the cemetery this path is fenced on both sides - so it is usable even when the cem. is closed. It's a public footpath believe it or not.
